reviewtext: I purchased this cable for my brand-new wireless printer after it didn't work so wirelessly after all. I leave the cable attached to the printer, and simply plug the USB into my laptop when I needed to print a document. The cable has worked great over the past several months. I did check my local electronic superstore before purchasing a cable via Amazon, but I found that comparable cables a ran a high dime. For its quality, you can't beat the price.
